proj4orderedlist

Class OrderedList<T extends java.lang.Comparable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • proj4orderedlist.OrderedList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Datatype that implements the Comparable interface.

    public class OrderedList<T extends java.lang.Comparable>
extends java.lang.Object
    OrderedList: a generic Linked List type of data structure that stores its items in ascending order based on their compareTo method. The type T stored in this class must implement the Comparable interface. Has methods for inserting new items, retrieving items at an index, removing items, etc.
